==English==

===Etymology===
From [[blog]] + [[alcoholic]]

===Noun===
'''blogoholic'''
# A person [[addicted]] to [[blogging]]

===Quotations===
*''A curious feature of "blogoholism" is that the amount of (otherwise potentially productive) time spent/wasted hopping from blog to blog is inversely proportional to the amount of blog entries one actually posts.'' - from a post entitled "Calm Sea," dated August 23, 2004, written by Frank MacGahon in his blog Internet Communicator.

